type InterestRate @entity @regularPolling {
  "Unique identifier for the interest rate entry"
  id: ID!
  "The interest rate value as a decimal"
  rate: BigDecimal!
  "The duration for which the interest rate is applicable, in some unit of time"
  duration: Int
  "The block number at which the interest rate matures"
  maturityBlock: BigInt
  "The side of the interest rate, indicating whether it is a borrowing or lending rate"

  type: InterestRateType!
  "The tranche associated with the interest rate, if applicable"
  tranche: Tranche
}"}
